task.summary: Default task
- Add root-user in DataBase and change the default Charset to 'utf8mb4'. - Update dependencies.
- Allow the 'picture' to be NULL in the DataBase and change the "Users"-column-order. - Add root-user creation in the DataBase. - Add "SpringFramework-version" in "build.gradle".
- Add "AppInstaller.sh"-script. - Code cleanup.
- New Feature: Allow users to upload a Profile Picture! - Increase the minimum allowed number of chars for passwords to <6>. - Add Input-"Validators" in SignIn & SignUp. - Code cleanup.
- Enhance profilePhotos-Storage-reliability by storing them with the unique "user_id". - Code cleanup.
- Add more Form-Validators (including password-confirmation). - Code cleanup.
Update ".idea" and "package-lock.json".
Update "Spring" and "SpringBoot".
- Add "Logback" as a logging implementation of SLF4J. - Set logging-levels in "application.properties". - Add logging-configuration-file: "logback-spring.xml".

New feature & optimizations (see details). - New feature: Backend for profile_photos-loading ready! - Update endpoints. - Add users' storage-directory. - Make file-paths platform-independent (use of "File.separator"). - Change admin's "picture" to "NULL" (this will be the default value in the DB, then the Backend will load the "generic_profile_photo,png"). - Code cleanup.
Downgrade "org.springframework.security" to v.5.0.8, as this package has not yet been updated to v.5.0.9 (otherwise all other Spring-dependencies used by Spring-Boot v.2.0.5 are in v.5.0.9).
Update "Gradle" to version: 4.10.1
Add execution-scripts.
- Admin now sees only regular-users in "home-admin", not itself. - Add "user.email" in users-view in "home-admin".

- Fix a bug where a non-imageType "profile_photo" was being send to the backend. - Leave the "user.picture=null" instead of assigning the "generic"-one, when the user has not selected a profile_photo during SignUp.
New Feature: Display user's profile_photos in "home-admin".
Handle case when user's profile_photo, was not found in storage, even though the user provided one. In this case, display the "image_not_found.png" instead.
- Update form-validators. - Initial "reset-picture"-code. - Code cleanup.
Resolve merge-conflicts.
Load user-profile_photo in "user-home".
- Add date-validator. - Guard "EducationForm"-submission against invalid factors. - Code cleanup.

- Navigate users and admin to their "homePage" instead of the general "welcomePage", when clicking the "Home-button". - Add the ability to "fix potential vulnerabilities" in the "AppInstaller.sh"-script.
Resolve conflicts.
Resolve more DataBase-conflicts.
Set every unknown path to redirect to the new "PageNotFoundComponent".
Keep the given-url in the address-bar when having a pageNotFound-error.
